post1: Such a crazy time with my bro from childhood. We got to this house party which was full of vibes. From the time we got there we knew it was going to be special. The decoration on the house was amazing. Massive shout out to whoever made the ribs, chicken wings and burgers - 10/10. Music was on point, dancing was on point too. We need to do this again.
post2: Just want to send a special happy birthday to my wife - my best friend, my advisor, my partner in crime and in love. Your patience, kind heart, focus, intelligence and your resilience in the face of life's obstacles makes me so lucky to be called your husband. To witness and stand by the woman you've grown into is amazing. I look forward to celebrating many more birthdays with you. Happy birthday my love.

post2: To my lovely and supportive partner, whose birthday it is today, I hope you have a lovely need and get everything you wish for, you certainly deserve it, you have been a wonderful partner to me and such a good father to our sons, where would we be without you, you always put us first and show us you care, it means the world to us to know we have your love and support.
